          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Transparent Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm">
            Detailed written quotes include everything — materials, labor, finishing. No surprise fees. Your estimate is your price.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
